T1	Participants 311 392	Hypertensive patients were randomized to measure HBP for 2 weeks or ABP for 24 h.
T2	Participants 521 772	Subjects with a difference of > or = 20 mm Hg systolic or > or = 10 mm Hg diastolic BP between CBP and awake ABP or CBP and HBP, were classified as clinic reactors. A total of 189 patients completed the study (79 on stable antihypertensive treatment).
